<h1>Vice Lobby Support</h1>

<p>Need help? We're here to assist you.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p>Email: orro.dev.team@gmail.com</p>

<p>For the fastest response, please include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Your device model</li>
  <li>Your operating system version</li>
  <li>A description of the issue</li>
  <li>Screenshots (if applicable)</li>
</ul>

<h2>Response Time</h2>

<p>We typically respond within 24–48 business hours.</p>

<h2>Common Topics</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Account and login issues</li>
  <li>Profile and photo problems</li>
  <li>Messaging or chat issues</li>
  <li>Crew or matchmaking questions</li>
  <li>Bug reports and technical support</li>
  <li>Feature requests and feedback</li>
</ul>

<h2>Bug Reports</h2>

<p>If you've found a bug, please tell us what happened and include the steps needed to reproduce the issue. This helps us resolve problems more quickly.</p>

<h2>Feedback</h2>

<p>We're always working to improve Vice Lobby. If you have ideas for new features or improvements, we'd love to hear from you.</p>

<h2>Thank You</h2>

<p>Thank you for being part of the Vice Lobby community.</p>

